=== Lessons for Future Research

The PACE trial illustrates how subjective outcomes, non-blinded design, mid-trial protocol changes, and broad case definitions can produce misleading results in ME/CFS research. Future trials should require: objective outcome measures (two-day CPET, actigraphy, biomarkers), PEM-requiring diagnostic criteria, independent outcome assessment, pre-registered protocols with locked outcome thresholds, and systematic PEM monitoring as a safety endpoint.


